cd mcp/[server-name]
npm update
npm install
```

**Testing Servers Manually:**
```bash
export SUPABASE_URL="..."
export SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="..."
node mcp/supabase/server.js
```

**Checking Logs:**
- Open Cursor Developer Tools (Help > Toggle Developer Tools)
- Check Console for MCP server output
- Server errors appear with `[MCP]` prefix

